1. *Pravda* je spora, ali dostižna. (Justice is slow, but achievable.)
2. On je uvek branio *pravdu*. (He always defended justice.)
3. Sud je doneo odluku u *pravdu* svih žrtava. (The court made a decision in the justice of all victims.)
4. Njegova želja za *pravdom* ga je dovela do borbe za ljudska prava. (His desire for justice led him to fight for human rights.)
5. Advokat će se boriti za *pravdu* svojih klijenata. (The lawyer will fight for the justice of his clients.)
6. Vlast mora da garantuje *pravdu* za sve građane. (The government must guarantee justice for all citizens.)
7. Nije fer da jedna osoba ima toliku moć da kontroliše *pravdu*. (It's not fair for one person to have so much power to control justice.)
8. *Pravda* će biti zadovoljena samo kada se kazne krivci. (Justice will be served only when the guilty are punished.)
9. On se nada da će jednog dana biti ostvarena *pravda* za njegovu porodicu. (He hopes that justice will one day be achieved for his family.)
10. Ova organizacija se bori za socijalnu *pravdu*. (This organization fights for social justice.)